<i>- ♪ Na, na, na, na, na, na ♪</i>

03:33.291 --> 03:34.750
<i>- ♪ One, two, three, four! ♪</i>

03:38.166 --> 03:40.166
[rock music]

03:40.208 --> 03:41.959
- Mae, would you like

03:40.208 --> 03:41.959
to read back

03:42.000 --> 03:43.000
the minutes from last meeting?

03:43.041 --> 03:44.834
- Yes.

03:44.875 --> 03:48.000
You asked if anyone had ideas

03:44.875 --> 03:48.000
for the spring festival,

03:48.041 --> 03:49.500
we all said "Nope,"

03:49.542 --> 03:52.542
then Natlee's "chair squeaked."

03:52.583 --> 03:54.458
Then we quickly adjourned.

03:56.500 --> 03:59.041
- Hey, is this

03:56.500 --> 03:59.041
"Student Events Club?"

03:59.083 --> 04:00.875
- What are you doing here?

04:00.917 --> 04:03.375
- I just thought this club

04:00.917 --> 04:03.375
could use some dude input.

04:06.458 --> 04:08.500
Ladies.

04:08.542 --> 04:10.834
- You know what?

04:08.542 --> 04:10.834
I don't have time to fight this.

04:10.875 --> 04:13.250
Okay, we have three days

04:10.875 --> 04:13.250
until the spring festival,

04:13.291 --> 04:15.000
and we need to raise money

04:13.291 --> 04:15.000
for our class trip,

04:15.041 --> 04:18.000
so let's think of some ideas.

04:18.041 --> 04:19.959
- How about a dance-a-thon?

04:18.041 --> 04:19.959
- We did that last year.

04:20.000 --> 04:21.458
- Walk-a-thon?

04:20.000 --> 04:21.458
- Eighth grade is doing that.

04:21.500 --> 04:23.458
- Skip-a-thon?

04:21.500 --> 04:23.458
- That's not a thing.

04:23.500 --> 04:26.500
- Then I got noth-on.

04:26.542 --> 04:28.208
- Come on, guys.

04:26.542 --> 04:28.208
We need to think.

04:28.250 --> 04:29.583
- Forget thinking.

04:29.625 --> 04:32.041
Just say the first thing

04:29.625 --> 04:32.041
that pops into your head.

04:32.083 --> 04:33.333
I'll start.

04:33.375 --> 04:35.333
Me in a kissing booth.

04:35.375 --> 04:37.250
Boom.

04:37.291 --> 04:40.959
Why don't we grab a smoothie

04:37.291 --> 04:40.959
and hammer out the details?

04:41.000 --> 04:42.834
- Dicky, we're trying to work.

04:42.875 --> 04:46.083
- So am I.

04:46.125 --> 04:48.083
- Look, this club is for people

04:48.125 --> 04:50.667
who are serious

04:48.125 --> 04:50.667
about helping the school.

04:50.709 --> 04:51.792
- Yeah,

04:50.709 --> 04:51.792
if you're not gonna help,

04:51.834 --> 04:53.000
you can just go sit in the back.

04:53.041 --> 04:54.417
- No, I'm gonna help.

04:54.458 --> 04:55.709
I'm sorry.

04:55.750 --> 04:59.125
[chair squeaks]

04:55.750 --> 04:59.125
It was the chair.

04:59.166 --> 05:01.917
- See?

05:01.959 --> 05:05.125
- Meeting adjourned!

05:08.917 --> 05:12.083
[mouthing words]

05:14.834 --> 05:17.792
[rock music]

05:17.834 --> 05:20.750
<i>♪ ♪</i>

05:20.792 --> 05:22.041
- Hey.

05:20.792 --> 05:22.041
- Ooh, uh, Mom?

05:22.083 --> 05:23.709
Can I get your opinion on these?

05:23.750 --> 05:25.333
- Oh, sure.

05:25.375 --> 05:27.834
Aww.

05:25.375 --> 05:27.834
[chuckles]

05:27.875 --> 05:29.000
Mmm.

05:29.041 --> 05:29.875
Delicious.

05:29.917 --> 05:32.250
- What are you doing?

05:32.291 --> 05:33.792
- What?

05:32.291 --> 05:33.792
You wanted my opinion!

05:33.834 --> 05:35.125
- This is my art project,

05:35.166 --> 05:38.583
not an all-you-can-eat

05:35.166 --> 05:38.583
panda buffet.

05:38.625 --> 05:40.959
- Sorry.

05:41.000 --> 05:42.917
- [sighs]

05:42.959 --> 05:45.375
- So are you gonna

05:42.959 --> 05:45.375
fix that little guy--

05:42.959 --> 05:45.375
- Just finish it.

05:42.959 --> 05:45.375
- Thank you.

05:45.959 --> 05:48.875
[rock music]

05:48.917 --> 05:51.417
- Ready... set...

05:51.458 --> 05:53.917
create!

05:56.000 --> 05:58.375
Create!

06:00.458 --> 06:04.000
Create!

06:04.041 --> 06:05.333
Ah!

06:04.041 --> 06:05.333
- Whoa.

06:05.375 --> 06:07.625
If you're going for mayonnaise

06:05.375 --> 06:07.625
in a snow storm,

06:07.667 --> 06:09.417
then you got it.

06:09.458 --> 06:10.875
- I got nothing!

06:10.917 --> 06:12.917
I'm trying,

06:10.917 --> 06:12.917
but without guidelines,

06:12.959 --> 06:14.083
I don't know where to start.

06:14.125 --> 06:16.583
- It's easy. Just do this.

06:16.625 --> 06:19.834
You've got a sky here...

06:19.875 --> 06:23.959
um... a little cottage there...

06:24.000 --> 06:25.959
some grass...

06:26.000 --> 06:27.542
a little tree-- oh!

06:27.583 --> 06:30.917
And how about a puppy?

06:30.959 --> 06:33.000
- I don't see

06:30.959 --> 06:33.000
any of those things,

06:33.041 --> 06:39.000
but it's amazing!

06:33.041 --> 06:39.000
- Yeah, it's pretty good.

06:39.041 --> 06:40.834
- I can't believe

06:39.041 --> 06:40.834
I'm saying this,

06:40.875 --> 06:44.542
but tell me

06:40.875 --> 06:44.542
your thought process.

06:44.583 --> 06:46.792
- Okay, well, step one,

06:44.583 --> 06:46.792
I grab a brush.

06:46.834 --> 06:48.917
Step two,

06:46.834 --> 06:48.917
I put some paint on it.

06:48.959 --> 06:50.959
Step three, I painted.

06:51.000 --> 06:53.000
Step four,

06:51.000 --> 06:53.000
you asked me how I did it.

06:53.041 --> 06:54.834
Step five, I told you.

06:54.875 --> 06:57.834
Step six,

06:54.875 --> 06:57.834
I go eat a burrito.

06:57.875 --> 07:00.333
- Wait, I can't even get

06:57.875 --> 07:00.333
to step three.

07:00.375 --> 07:02.625
This is due tomorrow,

07:00.375 --> 07:02.625
and I have nothing.

07:02.667 --> 07:04.166
- Just hand in mine.

07:04.208 --> 07:06.083
- I can't take credit

07:04.208 --> 07:06.083
for something I didn't do.

07:06.125 --> 07:08.625
- Oh. I respect that.

07:08.667 --> 07:11.125
I don't get it,

07:08.667 --> 07:11.125
but I respect it.

07:23.208 --> 07:26.333
- Okay. Step one,

07:23.208 --> 07:26.333
pick up the brush.

07:26.375 --> 07:30.417
[deep breath]

07:26.375 --> 07:30.417
Step two, put some paint on it.

07:30.458 --> 07:32.375
Step three...

07:33.917 --> 07:36.625
Step three...

07:36.667 --> 07:40.041
- Step three looks hard.

07:36.667 --> 07:40.041
- [gasps]

07:44.166 --> 07:45.875
- Hey, you know

07:44.166 --> 07:45.875
what my painting has

07:45.917 --> 07:47.917
that yours doesn't?

07:47.959 --> 07:50.333
Paint.

07:50.375 --> 07:53.750
Step four, laugh my way

07:50.375 --> 07:53.750
up the stairs.

07:53.792 --> 07:56.500
[laughs]

07:56.542 --> 07:59.917
- We'll see who has

07:56.542 --> 07:59.917
the last step four.

08:09.834 --> 08:12.166
Ricky...

08:12.208 --> 08:15.417
<i>[rock music]</i>

08:15.458 --> 08:16.917
<i>♪ ♪</i>

08:16.959 --> 08:21.125
- Your truth has moved me.

08:21.166 --> 08:23.917
I mean, the honesty,

08:21.166 --> 08:23.917
the bravery,

08:23.959 --> 08:26.875
in this hand turkey...

08:27.959 --> 08:31.125
I--

08:27.959 --> 08:31.125
I'm sorry, I can't!

08:31.166 --> 08:32.917
- Uh, Ms. Gressle?

08:32.959 --> 08:34.250
Where's my project?

08:34.291 --> 08:36.583
Uh, it was the panda rice balls.

08:36.625 --> 08:38.542
- I'm sorry.

08:36.625 --> 08:38.542
I didn't get them.

08:38.583 --> 08:41.583
- What? I left them

08:38.583 --> 08:41.583
on your desk this morning.

08:41.625 --> 08:44.166
- That's strange.

08:41.625 --> 08:44.166
but since it was food,

08:44.208 --> 08:46.333
it might have been

08:44.208 --> 08:46.333
taken away by rats.

08:46.375 --> 08:48.750
- Rats!

08:46.375 --> 08:48.750
- Or the janitor.

08:48.792 --> 08:50.166
- Mr. Katz!

08:50.208 --> 08:51.917
- I'll give you

08:50.208 --> 08:51.917
another day to redo it.

08:51.959 --> 08:54.959
- Redo it!

08:55.000 --> 08:56.917
- Ah, Dawn.

08:56.959 --> 09:00.750
Your painting is simply...

09:00.792 --> 09:04.417
mm, mm, mm!

09:05.709 --> 09:08.041
- Did you hear that, Ricky?

09:05.709 --> 09:08.041
My painting is...

09:08.083 --> 09:12.375
"Mm, mm, mm!"

09:12.417 --> 09:15.875
- Oh, and look at this one.

09:12.417 --> 09:15.875
[gasps]

09:15.917 --> 09:17.250
- Oh, that's mine.

09:17.291 --> 09:20.792
How does it sound,

09:17.291 --> 09:20.792
Ms. Gressle?

09:20.834 --> 09:23.667
- Ahhhhh!

09:23.709 --> 09:28.792
- Hear that?

09:23.709 --> 09:28.792
Mine's, "Ahhhhh!"

09:28.834 --> 09:33.375
- Um, excuse me,

09:28.834 --> 09:33.375
Ms. Gressle, "Mm--mm--mm!"

09:33.417 --> 09:36.750
Is better than, "Ahhhhh!"

09:33.417 --> 09:36.750
Right?

09:36.792 --> 09:40.208
- Dawn, I could never say

09:36.792 --> 09:40.208
that one piece

09:40.250 --> 09:44.000
is better than another,

09:40.250 --> 09:44.000
but in this case,

09:44.041 --> 09:47.542
one is better.

09:47.583 --> 09:50.917
In fact, I'm going to hang

09:47.583 --> 09:50.917
one of these paintings

09:50.959 --> 09:54.250
up in the hall right now.

09:55.166 --> 09:57.041
Dawn?

09:57.083 --> 09:58.875
- Yes, Ms. Gressle?

09:58.917 --> 10:02.083
- You're tall, come help me

09:58.917 --> 10:02.083
hang Ricky's painting

10:02.125 --> 10:05.834
up in the hall.

10:02.125 --> 10:05.834
- I don't think--

10:05.875 --> 10:08.834
- You know what my painting has

10:05.875 --> 10:08.834
that yours doesn't?

10:08.875 --> 10:12.625
You hanging it!

10:12.667 --> 10:14.250
- Ricky!

10:14.291 --> 10:17.500
<i>[rock music]</i>

10:17.542 --> 10:19.125
<i>♪ ♪</i>

10:19.166 --> 10:20.750
- Behold!

10:20.792 --> 10:23.709
[applause]

10:26.667 --> 10:29.625
- I believe it was Ms. Gressle

10:26.667 --> 10:29.625
who once said

10:29.667 --> 10:32.667
it was Picasso

10:29.667 --> 10:32.667
who once said,

10:32.709 --> 10:35.333
"Art is a lie...

10:35.375 --> 10:37.125
that tells the truth."

10:37.166 --> 10:40.333
[applause]

10:41.959 --> 10:45.834
- Speaking of "art" and "lies,"

10:41.959 --> 10:45.834
this doesn't add up.

10:45.875 --> 10:47.959
I'm not buying it.

10:45.875 --> 10:47.959
- It's not for sale.

10:48.000 --> 10:50.166
- We'll see about that.

10:51.291 --> 10:53.250
- This painting is so cool.

10:53.291 --> 10:55.417
- I didn't know

10:53.291 --> 10:55.417
Ricky could paint.

10:55.458 --> 10:57.291
- He's so talented!

10:57.333 --> 10:59.583
- I like a talented guy.

10:59.625 --> 11:00.959
- Oh, really?

11:01.000 --> 11:02.291
Well,

11:01.000 --> 11:02.291
what would you ladies say

11:02.333 --> 11:04.542
if I told you I painted that?

11:04.583 --> 11:07.709
[laughter]

11:04.583 --> 11:07.709
- Yeah, right, Dicky.

11:07.750 --> 11:09.125
- What, you think

11:07.750 --> 11:09.125
I couldn't paint that?

11:09.166 --> 11:11.500
- No, I know

11:09.166 --> 11:11.500
you couldn't paint that.

11:11.542 --> 11:13.959
- Yeah, you're

11:11.542 --> 11:13.959
"kissing booth" guy.

11:14.000 --> 11:16.625
- You never take

11:14.000 --> 11:16.625
anything seriously.

11:18.166 --> 11:19.834
- I take things seriously.

11:19.875 --> 11:21.500
- Oh, thanks

11:19.875 --> 11:21.500
for the painting, bro.

11:21.542 --> 11:22.917
- Yeah. I need it back.

11:22.959 --> 11:24.375
- What?

11:22.959 --> 11:24.375
- Dude.

11:24.417 --> 11:25.834
The girls love my painting.

11:25.875 --> 11:27.834
You gotta tell them

11:25.875 --> 11:27.834
that I painted it.

11:27.875 --> 11:29.083
- No, I can't do that.

11:29.125 --> 11:31.083
Then Ms. Gressle

11:29.125 --> 11:31.083
will know I lied.

11:31.125 --> 11:32.834
Besides, you said

